  "00_foundation/FOUNDATION.md": "# Foundation: Who are we?\n\n## 1. Corporate Identity\nWe are **Airwalk AI**. \nWe are **not** an \"AI bot agency\" or a \"chatbot factory.\" We are an **Operational AI Infrastructure Partner**.\n\n## 2. Core Purpose\nWe bridge the gap between experimental generative models and mission-critical enterprise systems. We replace fragile manual workflows with robust, observable, and secure agentic integration layers.\n\n## 3. Philosophy: Systems Engineering\n* **Observable Runtimes:** Every action is auditable, deterministic, and logs to local infrastructure.\n* **Security First:** Patient data, financial credentials, and client database logs are masked at the boundary.\n* **Immediate Delivery:** We prove value by delivering functioning MVPs in 14 days rather than selling 12-month consultative pipelines.\n",
