  "02_strategy/ICP.md": "# Syna Systems Ideal Customer Profile (ICP) Framework\r\n\r\n## Target Segment 1: The \"Operationally Strained\" Mid-Market (10-50 Employees)\r\n(Generalist Operational AI)\r\n\r\n### 1. The Core Signal: \"Hiring for Friction\"\r\n...\r\n## Target Segment 2: Healthcare Revenue Cycle Management (RCM)\r\n(Specialized Vertical: Denial Management)\r\n\r\n### 1. The Core Signal: \"Denial Attrition\"\r\nWe target Healthcare Groups and Hospitals (50-500+ staff) experiencing high first-pass denial rates:\r\n- **RCM Specialists/Analysts:** Hiring for roles focused on \"Denial Appeals\" or \"Billing Recovery.\"\r\n- **EHR Transitions:** Recent migration to Epic, Cerner, or Athenahealth (high risk of process friction).\r\n- **Consolidation:** Large healthcare groups acquiring smaller practices (need for unified billing infrastructure).\r\n\r\n### 2. Industry-Specific Pain Points\r\n- **Medical Necessity Denials:** Missing clinical documentation to support billing codes.\r\n- **Payer Rule Lag:** 30-90 day delays in updating billing rules to match payer policy shifts.\r\n- **Manual Appeals:** Senior staff spent 40+ hours/week writing custom appeal letters.\r\n\r\n### 3. Selection Criteria\r\n| Signal | Why it Matters | How to Find |\r\n| :--- | :--- | :--- |\r\n| **Hiring Billing Recovery** | High volume of denied revenue. | LinkedIn Jobs. |\r\n| **Athenahealth/Epic User** | High-volume EHR environments. | BuiltWith / Job Descs. |\r\n| **Medical Group (100+ MDs)**| Significant scale for ROI (1% = $Millions). | Industry filter. |\r\n| **Denial Management RFI** | Active search for infrastructure solutions. | Intent Data / Public RFIs. |\r\n\r\n## The \"Immediate Yes\" Value Proposition\r\n\"We eliminate healthcare denials at the source. Our **Predictive Denial Management** infrastructure turns 15% denial rates into 2% clean-claim performance. We don't just bill; we architect documentation integrity.\"\r\n",
