  "05_marketing/NEWSLETTER_SYSTEM.md": "# Newsletter System\n- **Core Topic:** Operational AI in Healthcare. Focused on denial metrics.",
  "05_marketing/WHITEPAPER_SYSTEM.md": "# Whitepaper Strategy\n- **Focus:** Technical specs on data pipeline security and agent orchestration.",
